{"lemma":"إِفادَةُ","slug":"إِفادَةُ","root":"ف.#.د","root_slug":"ف-_-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-_-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n34934"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A5%D9%90%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of أَفَادَ (ʔafāda) (form IV)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"advantage, gain","examples":[{"text":"فِي ٱلْإِعَادَةِ إِفَادَة"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"testimony","examples":[{"text":"أَدْلَى بِإِفَادَتِه","english":"he testified"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʔi.faː.da/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34934","headword_ar":"افادهُ","root":"fyd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, property, (AZ, Ks, T, S, M, O, L, K,) to another: (AZ, Ks, T, S, M, L:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AfAdhu maAlFA","text_ar":"افادهُ مَالًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ifaAdapN","text_ar":"اـِفَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave him property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb.) It belongs to this art. and to art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fwd","text_ar":"فود"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fwd","text_ar":"فود"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  [And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, profited, advantaged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"benefited, him;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAy^idapF","text_ar":"فَايِدَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"being understood. Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino A^afadotaniY HarofFA","text_ar":"اـِنْ اَفَدْتَنِى حَرْفًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faqado A^aSofadotaniY A^alofFA","text_ar":"فَقَدْ اَصْفَدْتَنِى اَلْفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If thou teach me a word, thou givest me"},{"kind":"text","text":"what is worth"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thousand"},{"kind":"text","text":"dirhems]. (A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sfd","text_ar":"صفد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  [Hence, also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AfAd","text_ar":"افاد"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a word, and a phrase,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It had,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"performed, a useful office, as expressive of a meaning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as contributing to the expression thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as adding to a meaning previously expressed."},{"kind":"text","text":"And hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It imported,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conveyed, a meaning;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly, when said of a phrase,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a complete meaning, so that a pause might be well made after uttering it;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAy^idapF","text_ar":"فَايِدَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"being understood.]       -A2-  See also 10. ―         -b2-  And see 1, last signification. ―         -b3-  Also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AfAdhu","text_ar":"افادهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He killed him; destroyed him; slaughtered him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a man, and a beast. (T, * L, and K * in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fwd","text_ar":"فود"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["AZ","Ks","T","S","M","O","L","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}